\FF[momoha_smile]Momoha: "Gotcha! Stop right there. I'm going to arrest
you~♪"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[momoha_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "A police officer strutting around inside the school
like they own the place...! It's not that dangerous here!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[momoha_smile]\AA[2]Momoha: "Oh? But isn't there a mysterious person attacking
others at large~? Must be quite a dangerous place, huh?"

\FF[momoha_reverse]Momoha: "Bingo~♪ Kyahaha!! Ahh, I am that mysterious
person~!! I just love attacking cute, cute high school girls
like you~♪"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[momoha_reverse]\AA[1]Akane: "The one who's supposed to protect is the
attacker...! It's quite distressing and subtly annoying!"
